<style>

    .logo-container {

    .logo-container img {
        max-width: 250px;
        max-height: 140px;
        color: goldenrod;
    }
    
    .logo-container-2 {
       flex-basis: 300px;
    }
    
    .title-text{
         text-shadow: -8px -2px 8px rgb(40 40 40 / 62%)

    @media all and (max-width: 1010px){

         .logo-container {
              flex-basis: 120px;

         .logo-container-2 {
               flex-basis: 210px;
          }
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 767px) {
        .logo-container {
            flex-basis: 60px;
        }
        
        .logo-container-2 {
            flex-basis: 120px;

            max-width: 50px;
            max-height: 80px;
        }
        
         .title-text{ font-size: 1.1rem; }
    }
    
    @media (max-width:419px) {

            flex-basis: 60px;
        }
        
        .logo-container-2 {
            flex-basis: 80px;
        }

            max-height: 110px;
